&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in relevant field or directly related experience; master’s degree or JD preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SHRM certification preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of ten (10) years of business experience in HR, operations, strategy, or related field&lt;/li&gt;
