&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or equivalency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CA Servsafe and Food Handlers Certification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of one (1) year of experience in food service or preparation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to prioritize in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
